{"tid":1918016,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"失業真係好正","createTime":"2020-03-09T23:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T05:09:11.000Z","uid":229185,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"83307a53f7157a04f8108b15b91dd00b1ab87c12","tid":1918016,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T23:35:38.000Z","msg":"每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命去返工,自己就懶懶閒嘆杯奶茶&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n食完早餐，返屋企上網搵工，每日send十封cv左右差唔多...<br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦，呢個世界大把免費娛樂&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n到左三四點，可能會覺肚餓，由於消耗唔多，可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包，或者食麥皮&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上，如果家人有煮飯就係屋企食，冇就盡可能自己煮，節省少少&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概以前返工四成左右,&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我以前辛苦返工 , 為既就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n但原來宜家失業已經可以做到，人生真係可笑，哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28aee40c6bdcf5bb30c04fa879e50ab3de86c399","tid":1918016,"uid":160348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T23:36:32.000Z","msg":"Send cv托咩"},{"pid":"e399a63c39e1c9f45a7132b9280d2ab09538dc17","tid":1918016,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28aee40c6bdcf5bb30c04fa879e50ab3de86c399","tid":1918016,"uid":160348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T23:36:32.000Z","msg":"Send cv托咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T23:38:39.000Z","msg":"準備攞失業救濟金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9281917ba2a89e0c8b9c8084739c1f26f0429d","tid":1918016,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T23:39:51.000Z","msg":"攞正牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal